name: US Navy pilots shot down Red Sea
summary: In a tragic incident, two US Navy pilots were shot down over the Red Sea in an apparent "friendly fire" incident. According to military officials, the pilots were flying an F/A-18 Super Hornet fighter jet when they were mistakenly targeted by another coalition aircraft. Both pilots managed to eject safely and were rescued by nearby vessels. The US military has expressed regret over the incident and is conducting an investigation to determine the exact circumstances that led to the friendly fire.
